&lt;p>Copper Extension is a simple Minecraft Mod for &lt;strong>Forge and Fabric&lt;/strong> witch adds a few features to the copper set&amp;hellip;&lt;/p>
&lt;p>The major feature is the rusty copper ingots. &lt;strong>Copper ingots can now be oxidixed in the inventory or even when you dropped it. And also they can be waxed&lt;/strong> using beehives or honeycombs&amp;hellip;&lt;/p></description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://killarexe.github.io/projects/copper-extension/feature.png"/></item><item><title>SPU</title><link>https://killarexe.github.io/projects/spu/</link><pubDate>Fri, 28 Apr 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://killarexe.github.io/projects/spu/</guid><description/></item><item><title>MSLang</title><link>https://killarexe.github.io/projects/mslang/</link><pubDate>Fri, 10 Feb 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://killarexe.github.io/projects/mslang/</guid><description>&lt;h1 class="relative group">About
