&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#about" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Little Rage is one of my biggest project in my entire carieer.&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>This game is a Solo platformer game based on speedrun and race. Made with the Godot game engine.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>You can unlock skins, hats and more&lt;/strong> by trying to make your best time in the levels. Also &lt;strong>you can share and make levels with the integrated level editor in the game!&lt;/strong>&lt;/p></description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://killarexe.github.io/projects/little-rage/feature.png"/></item><item><title>Dimensional Expansion</title><link>https://killarexe.github.io/projects/dimensional-expansion/</link><pubDate>Fri, 05 Mar 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://killarexe.github.io/projects/dimensional-expansion/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;a href="">
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://github.com/Killarexe/Dimensional-Expansion/raw/main/src/main/resources/logo.png" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">About:
&lt;div id="about" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#about" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>Dimensional Expansion is a Minecraft mod avaliable on Forge(maybe Fabric later) who adds new tools and weapons for your gears, blocks and for builders, items with special poperities and the main feature that is currenly in progress is a new dimension with dungeons, villages and other structures.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>The mod got currently an OST made by me(of course) that also working in progress but you can see some preview &lt;a href="https://soundcloud.com/killarexe" target="_blank">here&lt;/a>.&lt;/p></description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://killarexe.github.io/projects/dimensional-expansion/feature.png"/></item><item><title>Negative-N</title><link>https://killarexe.github.io/projects/negative-n/</link><pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://killarexe.github.io/projects/negative-n/</guid><description>&lt;h1 class="relative group">About
&lt;div id="about" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#about" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Negative-N is my first Minecraft Mod project.&lt;/strong> And for this I used called &lt;a href="https://mcreator.net/" target="_blank">&lt;strong>MCreator&lt;/strong>&lt;/a>. Witch is a software I still recommend to learn if you want to get into Minecraft Modding if you know nothing about coding.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>This Minecraft mod adds a &lt;em>new universe to Minecraft&lt;/em> and this universe adds mobs, minerals, exploration, adventure, crafting, blocks with interesting properties, technology, decoration, structures, a new mode of survival, nostalgia and beauty and more!&lt;/p></description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://killarexe.github.io/projects/negative-n/feature.png"/></item><item><title>Pokemon Mix</title><link>https://killarexe.github.io/projects/pokemon-mix/</link><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://killarexe.github.io/projects/pokemon-mix/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;strong>Pokemon Mix is my first game I&amp;rsquo;ve ever made&lt;/strong> using &lt;strong>RPG Maker XP&lt;/strong> and an old kit to make a Pokemon game called &lt;em>Pokemon essencials&lt;/em>.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>I&amp;rsquo;ve even made a launcher to execute different versions of this game. But around 6 months or 1 year later &lt;em>(I don&amp;rsquo;t know exactly)&lt;/em> I abandonned it beacause it was to big for a 1st project.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>I have still the source code of this game but it&amp;rsquo;s soo broken that I don&amp;rsquo;t want to share it. But maybe I&amp;rsquo;ll do a post about it.&lt;/p></description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://killarexe.github.io/projects/pokemon-mix/feature.jpg"/></item><item><title>About</title><link>https://killarexe.github.io/about/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://killarexe.github.io/about/</guid><description>&lt;h1 class="relative group">Who I&amp;rsquo;m I?
